snippet.title: Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 - Game of the Year Trailer I PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/marvels-spider-man-2/

The critically acclaimed and “Game of the Year” nominee (The Game Awards) Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 has new features now available via free patch update, including New Game+, Mission Replay Mode, New Accessibility Features, New Suits and more!

Spider-Men, Peter Parker and Miles Morales, return for an exciting new adventure in the Marvel’s Spider-Man franchise for the PS5 console. Equipped with Miles’ new bioelectric venom power and Peter’s Spider-Arms, the Spider-Men face the ultimate test of strength inside and outside the mask as they fight to save the city, each other and the ones they love, from the monstrous Venom. 

Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 is available now, only on PS5.

#ps5 #ps5games #spiderman2
